<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>New Signup Request</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Hello {{adminName}},</p>

    <p>A new user has requested access to your society portal. Here are the details:</p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{userName}}</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{userEmail}}</li>
      <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {{userPhone}}</li>
      <li><strong>Role:</strong> {{userRole}}</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Please <a href="{{adminPortalUrl}}">click here</a> to log in and approve the request.</p>

    <p>Regards,<br>Society Management Team</p>
  </body>
</html>
